        <fields>
            <name>Prescreen_Screen_Text_0_0</name>
            <fieldText>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 20px;&quot;&gt;Recruitment Process – Laboratory Support Placement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;You will be assessed at various stages throughout your application, these will include:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Your suitability statement (500 words)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Your application.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Your knowledge of the RFL and what we do.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Your first interview stage.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Your laboratory assessment stage.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Your face-to-face interview.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Due to the limited number of placements, we can offer, this will be a competitive recruitment process.&amp;nbsp;RFL operates to the highest standards, and we expect you to demonstrate this throughout the recruitment process.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Your suitability statement should demonstrate your knowledge of RFL, the skills and knowledge you will bring to your placement, why you should be selected to take part and what you hope to achieve through your time at RFL.&amp;nbsp;You should explain what motivates and interests you and what qualities you have that will add value to RFL.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;If you are involved in groups which add value to your local community, undertake activities which support local or national charities or have other interests which demonstrate your citizenship, please ensure you include these.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;As part of the recruitment process, you will undertake a laboratory-based assessment including sample receipt, unbagging and checking samples prior to processing &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;and pipetting concluding with a face-to-face interview.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Please download and complete the application documents below. You will be asked to upload these at a later stage in the online application process:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://impellam.my.salesforce.com/sfc/p/#0Y000000LzSj/a/4J000000d0sY/6ygdrwWM81AEbxNvYPzaZUzcVYU2xKvTkGKDu47sbkc&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Job Description&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://impellam.my.salesforce.com/sfc/p/#0Y000000LzSj/a/4J000000d0xT/jPdGblpdetgGi3ZitrNAwxUpwWRyOxXWN5cCOJPm46U&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Application Form&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</fieldText>
            <fieldType>DisplayText</fieldType>
        </fields>
        <nextOrFinishButtonLabel>Get Started</nextOrFinishButtonLabel>
        <showFooter>true</showFooter>
        <showHeader>false</showHeader>
